summary.headline: Six-month silence stalls auditorium platform after accelerating delivery
summary.summary: The project previously demonstrated accelerating momentum with 20 commits delivering Azure integration, conflict detection, and admin tooling driven by Lalithaditya007, shivv-byri, and Slaltihaditya-23071A12B9. Now the repository has flatlined, with the main branch dormant for 191 days and zero commits in the last week. No active contributors, open PRs, or issues indicates the team disbanded completely rather than pausing mid-sprint. This abrupt abandonment risks losing the synchronized progress across frontend, backend, and cloud infrastructure.
highlights: Azure cloud storage integration and dynamic venue creation features remain in codebase
Robust booking conflict detection and admin notification systems previously implemented
Clean repository state with no lingering open PRs or unresolved technical debt
concerns: 191-day development halt with zero contributor activity after accelerating velocity
Complete team abandonment with no open issues or PRs to indicate return plans
Risk of knowledge loss as the multi-contributor synchronization breaks down
summary.recommendation: Reconvene Lalithaditya007, shivv-byri, and the previous contributor team immediately to confirm project resumption plans or formally archive the repository.

summary.headline: Frontend infrastructure complete but project dormant for 30 days
summary.summary: The repository shows zero commits in the past week and has been dormant for 30 days since ch-praneeth-08's last push to main. ch-praneeth-08 remains the sole contributor, having authored all 4 commits, but development activity stopped in late January. This creates a single-point-of-failure risk combined with a complete halt in momentum despite completed technical setup. The project lacks current development velocity toward launch readiness.
highlights: Production-ready infrastructure with Vite tooling and environment-based API configuration
Vercel deployment pipeline and CORS configuration operational
Clean repository state with zero open issues or PRs requiring attention
concerns: 30 days of zero commit activity indicates development has halted
Single-contributor dependency with ch-praneeth-08 as the only developer
No current velocity despite completed scaffolding
summary.recommendation: Schedule an immediate sync with ch-praneeth-08 to unblock development or reassign resources.
